skdetail:

Invocation Name: coffee round
des: Next time you're trying to decide whose turn it is pick something or perform a task, just ask Alexa for help. Give each person a number from one to three and Alexa will randomly choose who's turn it is.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
